// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// G.11 — Public School Landing Site content.
// These rows make the school subdomain site real and editable instead of a
// hardcoded one-page placeholder. All rows are tenant-owned and public reads only
// expose rows with `published = true` / `status = PUBLISHED`.
