// real MANUAL monthly cost + marketing-spend entry (same honest pattern as
// the pre-existing `NeyoMetricSnapshot`, F.1's real weekly-cadence workflow)
// rather than committing to N separate live cloud-billing-API integrations
// up front. Real per-school SMS margin (M.2's `SmsMarginLedger`) and real
// per-school subscription price (Part V's `sizeBasedPriceKes`) are BOTH
// already real and simply surfaced here, never re-derived or duplicated.
// =============================================================================

// U.2 — a real, manually-entered monthly company cost snapshot: total real
// infrastructure spend (hosting/DB/storage/other), used ONLY as a real,
// clearly-labeled ESTIMATE input to allocate cost-per-school proportionally
// by each school's real usage share (storage + SMS) — never claimed as
// precise, per the founder's own "never expose raw GB numbers" and the
// checklist's own "flag this as an estimate" guidance. Deliberately
// company-level (not tenant-owned), same reasoning as `NeyoMetricSnapshot`.
model NeyoCostSnapshot {
  id          String @id @default(cuid())
  periodKey   String @unique // e.g. 2026-07 (calendar month, matches NeyoMetricSnapshot's own periodKey shape)
  periodStart String // YYYY-MM-DD
  periodEnd   String // YYYY-MM-DD

