  // (KES) — hosting/compute, database, file storage, and any other real
  // recurring infra bill NOT already tracked per-school (SMS is EXCLUDED
  // here since it already has its own real per-school ledger, SmsMarginLedger,
  // and must never be double-counted).
  infraCostKes Int @default(0)

